# NGSmodule Backend - dev/test dependencies
#
# Includes everything from requirements.in plus tooling for development,
# testing, formatting, linting, and type checking.
#
# Edit this file, then run:
#   pip-compile --output-file=requirements-dev.txt requirements-dev.in

# Use prod lock as version constraint, so dev/prod stay in sync.
# When you bump a prod dep in requirements.in + recompile requirements.txt,
# rerun pip-compile here too.
-c requirements.txt
-r requirements.in

